es are found in studying the upturn effect of\nsolar neutrino oscillation, light sterile neutrinos, and Earth matter effect.\nThe sensitivities in discovering solar neutrino upturn and light sterile\nneutrinos are shown.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Mar 2022 17:13:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 28 Mar 2022 14:11:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-29"}
