term, or to fully automate log picking\noperations in the future.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Mar 2022 18:29:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 18 Oct 2022 21:57:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-20"}
