 and qualitative analysis of the results. The\nusefulness and effectiveness of LegalVis were evaluated through two usage\nscenarios and feedback from six domain experts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Mar 2022 20:33:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-17"}
