 frequencies above 1 Hz. The testing\non real-time hardware revealed that both PV and PLL have marginal impact on\nmicrocontroller load, while the efficiency of the PV was 4% lower than the PLL.\nActive auditory stimulation did not influence the phase tracking. This work\ndemonstrated that phase-accurate auditory stimulation can be delivered during\nhome-based sleep interventions with a wearable device also in populations with\nlow-amplitude SW.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Mar 2022 14:42:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-01"}
